al'. Broadcast on NPR</a> Jan. 25 (during All Things Considered program)<br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><a title=\"http://whyy.org/cms/radiotimes/2015/12/07/productivity-and-distraction-in-the-workplace/\" href=\"http://whyy.org/cms/radiotimes/2015/12/07/productivity-and-distraction-in-the-workplace/\">Radio Times Interview, Productivity and Distraction in the Workplace. WHYY, NPR, Philadelphia and NPR Sirius.</a> Aired December 7, 2015.<br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\">NPR Marketplace. Interview with host Ben Johnson. Codebreaker--Is it Evil? Episode 1: Email. Nov. 11, 2015<br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><a onclick=\"window.open(this.href); return false;\" title=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2015/05/why-some-people-cant-stand-having-unread-emails/394031/\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2015/05/why-some-people-cant-stand-having-unread-emails/394031/\" onkeypress=\"window.open(this.href); return false;\">The Atlantic. Inbox Zero vs. Inbox 5,000: A Unified Theory. May 27, 2015. </a><br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><br /></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><a title=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/business-32628753\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/business-32628753\">BBC News. Losing focus: Why tech is getting in the way of work. May 8, 2015.<br /></a></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><a title=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/business-32628753\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/business-32628753\"><br /></a></p>\n                  <p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><a title=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/29/opinion/end-the-tyranny-of-24-7-email.html?_r=0\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/29/opinion/end-the-tyra